title: November Debuts: Give No Thanks for Not Reading a LOT of comics!
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.

The month being glorious November 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, heh.

This instalment contains the following current debuts:


   Dark Gods        #1        - Avatar        - Action / Horror / Supernatural
   Deep State       #1        - Boom Studios  - Alternate Reality / Mystery / Sci-Fi
   Drifter          #1        - Image         - Adventure / Mystery / Sci-Fi
   Man vs Rock      #1        - (Independent) - Disaster / Humour / Pulp
   Penny Dora       #1        - Image         - Fantasy / Humour / Mystery
   Resurrectionists #1        - Dark Horse    - Crime / Historical / Sci-Fi
   Terrible Lizard  #1 (of 5) - Oni           - Adventure / Historical / Sci-Fi
   The Kitchen      #1 (of 8) - Vertigo       - Crime / Drama / Noir
   Tooth and Claw   #1        - Image         - Adeventure / Disaster / Fantasy


Nice haul, huh? And, just to make that lot even more of a lot, there are again bonuses, too, of course! As it happens, they're very similar to last month's; namely, the two full-length debuts corresponding to the two previously included previews. For Dark Horse's "Ghost Fleet", the preview turned out to be just an excerpt from the debut proper. For Aspen's "ZooHunters", on the other hand, the preview turned out to be all-original, so I re-added that one as well. Enjoy! :D
